<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>footwork • leg work</xh5><p> <i>footwork—</i>sureness and accurate placing of the feet in boxing, dancing, etc.: Kaman makes the most of his <u>footwork</u>. He stays clear of Tosca and picks his punches well.</p><p> <i>leg work—</i>1. <i>= footwork: </i>Flying wings rely on the pilot’s <u>legwork</u> to become airborne and span and performance is limited by the power of the human shoulder. 2. work which involves running errands or going from place to place: Patey was no man of action, but he might send a man we used a great deal for <u>leg work</u>.</p> </entry>
